25.text:
In the sacred alcove where prayers ascend,
A box of reverence, where solace blends.
Gaze upwards, where angels might tread,
On the right-hand path, a clue is spread.

Beyond eye's reach, a festive light gleams,
Ascend to the top, where the mystery teems.

26.title: 🎁
26.text:
Wrapped in red and silver bright,
I wait in silence through the night.
Where lists are kept and plans are made,
Look to the board where notes are laid.
